text: Duncan Fisher (17 July 1962 - 23 December 1984) was an Australian rower. He competed in the men's coxless four event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. He was killed in a car crash. ==References== Category:1962 births Category:1984 deaths Category:Australian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Australia Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
